@description.name: @description
@description.body: Returns the number of cells in this grid

@description.name: @description
@description.body: Add a SVGElement to a cell in the grid.

@param.name: @param
@param.body: row {number} row number (-1 to find next free row)
@param.description: row number (-1 to find next free row)

@param.name: @param
@param.body: column {number} column cumber (-1 to use next free cell)
@param.description: column cumber (-1 to use next free cell)

@param.name: @param
@param.body: replace {boolean} it true replace current item in cell, otherwise the element will not be added when the cell is not empty
@param.description: it true replace current item in cell, otherwise the element will not be added when the cell is not empty

@param.name: @param
@param.body: retries {number} internal value used to limit layout retries for one element. Do not set this externally!
@param.description: internal value used to limit layout retries for one element. Do not set this externally!
